title: Home Behind v1.135
description: In Home Behind, you take on the role of a refugee cast out from your homeland by a band of rebels. Your home and the peace you enjoyed has been destroyed, and your family has disappeared. Can you survive the struggle, famine, and sickness to make it to the safety of Europe?The thoughts of civil war had been brewing in your homeland for years, and the violence has finally erupted.
